CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg. 1 reads:"President Kennedy Stumps Area for Democrats - McKeesport's high school band is shown as it participated in salute to the President."
TitMainTitle: McKeesport High School marching band standing at attention, with sharpshooters on roof tops and Union Clothing Co. billboard in background, for President Kennedy campaign stop, near Lysle Boulevard, McKeesport, Pennsylvania
